  "name": "Gritz: The Pyramid Adventure",
  "shortName": "gritz-the-pyramid-adventure",
  "description": "<i>Gritz: The Pyramid Adventure</i> is a game about adventurers from four different countries, Mexico, England, Israel and Zaire who travel to Egypt to find secrets and treasures in the pyramids. The game play is similar to <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?game=bomberman\">Bomberman</a>. Players try to avoid getting washed down drains in the maze and other players to to get their opponents to fall into traps they set. There is a VS mode, where up to 4 human players can play with the use of the Multitap. There is also a story mode where the player chooses one of the 4 main characters and goes through the 8 floors of the pyramid. ",
